comments: Lopez (MIL) sets the screen on Gordon (HOU) and does not deliver contact.
Ilyasova (MIL) moves into Harden (HOU) and makes contact with his body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Lopez (MIL) makes marginal contact with Tucker (HOU) as he makes his post move.
Tucker (HOU) makes contact with Lopez's (MIL) arm and affects his shot attempt.
Middleton (MIL) makes clean contact with the ball while defending Westbrook's (HOU) shot attempt.
Tucker (HOU) maintains a legal guarding position while defending Lopez (MIL) in the post.
Tucker (HOU) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Lopez (MIL) and makes clean contact with the ball.
Ilyasova (MIL) initiates contact with Harden (HOU) that affects his ability to control the rebound.
Harden (HOU) maintains a legal guarding position on Bledsoe (MIL) at the start of the drive.
Middleton (MIL) is stationary and establishes his left foot as his pivot foot.  He then slides his pivot foot prior to releasing the pass.
Gordon (HOU) makes marginal contact with Middleton (MIL) and does not affect his SQBR.
Middleton (MIL) releases the ball before stepping into the backcourt.
Matthews (MIL) maintains a legal guarding position on Gordon (HOU) during the drive.
Matthews (MIL) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Gordon (HOU).
